ube睇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似好正</blockquote><br />\n係呀，如果將來要用黎present 可以買舊docking 插hdmi 連接個瑩幕幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗好就去下電器鋪或者mic記官網睇下有無做暑期優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該join back to school 個個scheme買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望下個sem gpa爆到4"},{"pid":"27b77f09da77da991536a71c3f7fd8a28447dd51","tid":328051,"uid":120859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好驚佢出藍mon個啲野</blockquote><br />\n邊有咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nxp 有試過，但係win 7打後我真係冇試過藍mon</blockquote><br />\n岩岩去左睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSurface pro好似laglag地機</blockquote><br />\n我用部sp3又唔覺得lag <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係我要求低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過買電腦最緊要自己啱心水架啫<br />\nmacbook 又好 surface 又好，兩部都好用<br />\n你試完鐘意邊部多d咪買邊部囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果好似我咁慣左手寫jot note，或者多用ebook，sp 係方便好多<br />\nbtw 買sp 嘅話sp4 好似抵d，因為新sp 唔跟筆 (但係新果支係好寫d，同apple penril 有得比)，同埋sp4 i5 以上送keyboard(另外買都要成千蚊) <br />\ni5 128gb 4g ram 依家特價7000蚊，夠你用架啦)</blockquote><br />\nGb數唔洗大啲？？😖<br />\n我諗住睇下佢有無學生優惠個啲<br />\n睇下會唔會送埋<br />\nSp4好似得藍色😳😳</blockquote><br />\n係喎，應該有學生優惠喎<br />\n我果時部sp3都係學生優惠買，好似六千三<br />\n藍色都唔錯架，粉粉地咁<br />\n不過我都係買左紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGB 數你指harddisk？當然大d好d，不過會貴d。如果普通文書，搵書用128gb 都ok 架啦，當然如果學生價大容量果d唔係大貴好多就有大食大啦。<br />\n不過如果你dl 劇或者擺相嘅話就可以買個外置harddisk，幾百蚊都有成1tb (嘅係差唔多1000 gb)。(平咁多係因為外置harddisk 係hdd，比sp 內置嘅ssd 慢好多，但係純粹storage hdd 夠哂用)</blockquote><br />\n定你指ram ？<br />\n其實最理想就8 gb ram，但4 ram 都唔會有問題，都係順嘅<br />\n不過最緊要睇餸食飯啦，始終升一級就幾舊水</blockquote><br />\n唔該曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日都有睇埋macbook pro灰黑色<br />\n真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以一萬之內搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb906e91203462075c7f32c6390c00e14bcd8f0","tid":328051,"uid":86345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"用緊sp4 什少用支筆抄野 始終都係唔太準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過部機勝在輕"}]}